      "chunk_length": 82,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.305287"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "But the pandemic has also highlighted a more worrying issue called compassion fatigue. Have you heard of that, Sam? Yes, I think compassion fatigue is a kind of emotional exhaustion which reduces your ability to empathise or feel compassion for others.",
      "chunk_id": "eb920363-de02-4f88-aef3-5fa064835db4",
      "chunk_index": 1,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 252,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "BI",
        "LED",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.307657"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "We'll be hearing how the suffering and unhappiness we see on the TV news can increase feelings of helplessness.",
      "chunk_id": "a9f281e5-e46e-4421-ac7c-83ec5a5fe537",
      "chunk_index": 2,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 111,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "PPI",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.309853"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "OK, Sam, we'll find out the answer later on. Compassion fatigue centres on the idea that we can feel too much empathy and that feeling can lead",
      "chunk_id": "88cc59e6-d027-49a8-bf54-0b10a6156026",
      "chunk_index": 3,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 143,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.312058"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "to emotional burnout. Well, here's Margaret Heffernan talking to BBC World Service's The Documentary podcast. See if you can hear the effects of compassion fatigue she mentions.",
      "chunk_id": "bec6006a-b63d-4b39-b22d-1706238e75cd",
      "chunk_index": 4,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 177,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.314347"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Margaret Heffernan mentions that",
      "chunk_id": "ff7f4a88-65be-48ba-99b1-31073afdef6c",
      "chunk_index": 5,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 32,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.316413"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "This is all incredibly depressing, Rob. It sounds like we have limited amounts of compassion. Well, there are more positive ways of looking at it, Sam.",
      "chunk_id": "7432c6c0-4c3f-420b-882c-3d74281a98b4",
      "chunk_index": 6,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 151,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.318624"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "I understand why you're saying that it's finite, but I also think compassion is a habit. So dwelling with that, developing that habit, yes, there are a lot of headwinds to that and the rapid acceleration of the news cycle, the focus on the next problem so quickly draws our attention away from developing those deeper habits as humanity that gives us that courage",
      "chunk_id": "5318f4e0-4f6e-47bd-9d44-6fe80fc6022f",
      "chunk_index": 7,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 363,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "UI",
        "BI",
        "專業技能",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.321123"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "and that strength to make these big transformations.",
      "chunk_id": "7b4aa4e5-15fb-4ecc-a764-35defbd87933",
      "chunk_index": 8,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
