      "enhanced_tags": [
        "BI",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.323199"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Maybe the answer is to help in whatever ways we can without becoming hard-hearted.",
      "chunk_id": "2e118b53-c7ea-4e09-8dbb-e7709f94fa62",
      "chunk_index": 9,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 82,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.325336"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Like the volunteers of MSF. Yes, your quiz question, Rob. You asked what the French name Medecins Sans Frontières means in English and I said B, Doctors Without Borders. Which was the correct answer. Well done. OK, Rob, let's recap the vocabulary, starting with",
      "chunk_id": "fee7f88c-133c-47a0-af6c-1e95fcfbf919",
      "chunk_index": 10,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176645",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_Compassion fatigue.json",
