        "AI"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.329959"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Which can be a headwind or opposing force which stops us caring for others. And that's it for this edition of 6 Minute English. Bye for now. Bye.",
